00:19:07.570 --> 00:19:09.820
What do you think is “the right” way

00:19:10.010 --> 00:19:12.700
to define who becomes a citizen or not?

00:19:13.060 --> 00:19:15.180
Do I deserve my Italian citizenship,

00:19:15.520 --> 00:19:17.320
or is the country handing

00:19:17.340 --> 00:19:18.910
out passports too liberally?

00:19:19.430 --> 00:19:21.080
I would love to know, so let’s

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:22.470
get this discussion started.

00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:24.190
Let me know in the comments below,

